DLW-SPUN · the full weave of Kharl

who   : A Brystan cooper turned self-made ordermage, an artisan who never sought power.
what  : A cooper who becomes an ordermage.
where : Brysta and Austra — Wellspring of Chaos, Ordermaster.
why   : Injustice drives him from barrel-staves to power he never asked for.
when  : The later age of Recluce and Austra — Wellspring of Chaos and Ordermaster.
how   : Self-taught order from a single found book, tested in exile.

class : Order · Black · the discipline of Recluce
